Package: reviewerguideR
Title: ADRG and cSDRG Draft Creation Harness
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: c(
    person(given = "reviewerguideR", family = "contributors", role = c("aut", "cre"), email = "noreply@example.com")
  )
Author: reviewerguideR contributors
Maintainer: reviewerguideR contributors <noreply@example.com>
Description: Creates basic ADRG and cSDRG draft reviewer guides from structured
    metadata such as define.xml and validation finding files. The MVP is
    evidence-bound, deterministic in dry-run mode, and avoids external LLM or
    embedding calls during automated tests.
